"The Incredible Machine"  Release Notes (version 1.0)

Keyboard Controls

1-9, a-g        Changes music in Freeform Mode

ALT-V           Brings up version number from Control Panel

TAB             Moves cursor between hotspots

Arrows          Moves cursor anywhere on the screen

Space, Enter    Same as pushing the left mouse button

Esc             Brings up Control Panel

X,Y             Flips a shape

+,-             Sizes a shape





